We've been watching a back-and-forth battle here,

23
00:02:56,870 --> 00:02:59,150
but everything will be decided by this final match!

24
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:06,830
Now, the final battle will begin!

25
00:03:12,420 --> 00:03:15,340
Representatives from both teams enter the ring!

26
00:03:15,340 --> 00:03:21,340
["Love Is Unconditional"]

27
00:03:29,380 --> 00:03:30,310
Shinpachi.

28
